playstore_details.title: Heart Rate: Blood Pressure App
playstore_details.description:
Heart Rate: Blood Pressure App is the most accurate, efficient, and easy-to-use heart rate monitor and blood pressure recorder.
Get your pulse result in just a few seconds anywhere, anytime — no other equipment required. By closely monitoring your heart rate and blood pressure, it helps you understand your body, assesses the readings, and provides improvement suggestions — this is the comprehensive health tracker you are looking for.

Here’s what we’ve got for you:
❤️ Accurate pulse measurement in seconds
🤳 Blood pressure tracker right at hand
📊 Detailed history, graphs and stats
📚 Reliable health tips and insights
📨 Health report sharing with doctors in just one tap

Why should I track heart rate and blood pressure?
Regularly tracking your heart rate and blood pressure helps detect any potential health risks or abnormalities early. Furthermore, our science-based health insights provide a broad understanding of your body and offer improvement tips, thus contributing to your better overall well-being.

Are the heart rate results accurate?
We employ reliable PPG (photoplethysmography) technology. Simply place your fingertip in front of the camera and keep it steady for a few seconds. By detecting changes in the color and brightness of the blood vessels in your fingertip, your phone's camera accurately measures your heart rate.

How to track my blood pressure?
Just input your blood pressure readings, and you will get the result automatically to see if they are within the normal range.

How often should I record health data?
For a comprehensive understanding of your health, it's advisable to maintain long-term records and track your health data multiple times a day in various states — after getting up, after meals, after exercise sessions, etc. We will generate easy-to-understand charts that visually display your trends and fluctuations. Additionally, you can gain deeper insights into your body by swiftly filtering the results.

Disclaimer:
- This app shall not serve as a substitute for professional medical advice.
- This app is intended for educational and informational use only.
- In case of any health concerns, please seek immediate medical attention.
- The flashlight may be hot during measurements, please avoid touching it.
- We are not able to and will never scan or use your fingerprint.
